These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, freelancer, musician
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the freelancer##1
2. the musician is between the fan of pop and the freelancer##2
3. the designer is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Job      | freelancer | musician | designer |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
City: rome, london, hamburg
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to rome and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| City     | london | hamburg | rome         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, martial-arts
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
2. the person watching adventure movies is between the owner of the ferret and the person watching martial-arts movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | adventure     | martial-arts |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, blue, fuchsia
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person who likes orange is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person who likes fuchsia is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Color   | blue  | fuchsia     | orange |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, animation, musical
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | musical     | western |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, may, december
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person who's birthday is in december and the person who's birthday is in september##2
2. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Birthday   | september  | may   | december        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, indie, metal
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the fan of punk is between the person eating pineapple and the fan of indie##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Music-Genre   | indie | punk | metal     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, western
There 3 different types of food: carrot, asparagus, banana
1. the person watching satire movies is the person eating banana##1
2. the person eating asparagus is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | comedy  | satire  |
| Food   | carrot | asparagus | banana |

