.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different pets are kept: mouse, turtle, hedgehog
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the owner of the hedgehog and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Pet       | hedgehog | mouse | turtle  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

