The people use 3 different means of transport: car, motorbike, quad-bike
1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
2. the person drinking fanta is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person drinking cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Beverage         | coffee | fanta | cola |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

