.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, bus, roller
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person driving the bus and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the person driving the roller is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Transport   | bus | van      | roller      |
| Food       | kale  | zucchini | blueberry |

